<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٠٨٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">‌قَتَادَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">‌أَنَسٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«رُخِّصَ لِعَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنِ عَوْفٍ، وَالزُّبَيْرِ فِي الْقَمِيصِ الْحَرِيرِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>